text: Vito Damiano (born 23 November 1952 in Trapani) is an Italian politician. He was appointed generale di brigata of the Carabinieri in 2007 and served as Mayor of Trapani from 2012 to 2017. ==References== ==See also== *2012 Italian local elections *List of mayors of Trapani ==External links== * * Category:Mayors of Trapani Category:1952 births Category:Living people
